Tony: *sees Thor with short hair and beard* oh sweet mother of God fuck me please
Tony: *sees Bucky with longer hair and beard*...
body:
Tony: *sees Thor with short hair and beard* oh sweet mother of God fuck me please

Tony: *sees Bucky with longer hair and beard* oh fuck me daddy

Tony: *sees Steve in all his beard glory* beard Jesus needs to fuck me too

Tony: *sees Sam rocking facial hair* noooooo not you too

Meanwhile….

Bruce: is he alright?

Stephen: yeah ever since I met, apparently I have given him a facial hair kink so he turns into a horny dog when he sees it.

Bruce: Clint better watch out then

Stephen: why’s that?

Bruce: *shows a photo of Clint with facial hair*

Stephen: I guess Loki better watch out too *shows a photo of Thor and Loki rocking facial hair*

Bruce: I’m glad I don’t have facial hair

Stephen: why’s that?

Bruce: because of that *points to Tony who has thrown Bucky to the ground and is sitting on him as he furiously rubs his face against Bucky’s*

Stephen: I’ll go save them

-6 minutes later

Bruce drags Tony off of a blushing Stephen and takes him away from the facial hair crew.

Tony is kicking and screaming because he needs his facial hair fix.

Sam: I have a plan

Everyone looks at each other before bowling each other over trying to get to the shavers in the bathroom.

Vision: does this usually happen?

Nat: I don’t know but it is hilarious and I need to stop those guys from shaving because we need some fun back in this place

Wanda: *uses magic* already way ahead of ya

-in the background

Bruce: NO TONY STAY AWAY FROM QUI- DAMMIT TONY
